p in the ultra-luxury private villa market.", "experiences/0/jobStartedOn": "11-2024", "experiences/0/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/0/title": "General Manager", "experiences/1/companyName": "ÀNI Private Resorts, Thailand", "experiences/1/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/1/jobDescription": "Overseeing and led daily operations across all departments to deliver a seamless, ultra-luxury experience, upholding ANI’s high service standards through refined SOPs and personalized guest care. Led and train a high-performing team, ensure pristine property maintenance, and coordinate bespoke guest services. I manage procurement and inventory of premium products while maintaining compliance with regulations and controlling costs. \n\nCollaborating with the General Manager, we collaborated to enhance the brand experience and provide data-driven insights to improve operations, guest satisfaction, and financial performance.", "experiences/1/jobEndedOn": "11-2024", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "5-2022", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/1/title": "Operations Manager", "experiences/2/companyName": "La Vela Khaolak", "experiences/2/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "Successfully led the sales team to achieve strong growth and consistently meet targets by designing strategic sales plans that expanded the customer base and enhanced market presence. Together with the team we built lasting relationships with repeat customers and monitored emerging markets and competitors to stay ahead. Additionally, we collaborated with guests and hotel departments to create engaging events and managed content across social media platforms—including Facebook, Instagram, and LINE—to boost brand visibility and engagement.", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "12-2021", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "7-2019", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/title": "Assistant Sales &  Event Manager", "experiences/3/companyId": "6616771", "e